wobani.core

Class Component

  • java.lang.Object
    • wobani.core.Component
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ComponentBase, Invalidatable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AudioListenerComponent, AudioSourceComponent, BlinnPhongLightComponent, CameraComponent, EnvironmentProbeComponent, RenderableComponent

    public abstract class Component
extends java.lang.Object
implements ComponentBase
    All of a GameObject's Components based on this abstract class. The GameLoop call it's update method once a frame, before rendering.
